  • Related Packages

    Description
    com.telenav.kivakit.resource
     
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    InputResource
    An InputStream stream wrapper that allows *one-time* reading of an input stream as a ReadableResource.
    NullResource
    A writable resource that accepts anything you write and destroys it, so when you read there is nothing to be seen.
    OutputResource
    An OutputStream stream wrapper that turns the output stream into a WritableResource.
    ResourceSection
    A portion of a resource from one offset into the resource to another.
    StringOutputResource
    A WritableResource that writes to a byte array, and can be converted to a string with StringOutputResource.string().
    StringResource
    A ReadableResource formed from a string passed to the constructor StringResource(String).
